{"tid":425574,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"on撚9，原來香港既「美食車」都係用中央廚房！","createTime":"2017-10-05T23:49:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-07T08:47:26.000Z","uid":29314,"like":40,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":74,"replies":[{"pid":"b699132dca4707bf8b64942fab5e4f007b1b44aa","tid":425574,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T23:49:22.000Z","msg":"計劃日前再「流多一滴血」，出現首架開業後退出的美食車。<br />\n<br />\n熟悉業界人士向老紀透露，該車為主打芝士三文治的「Creative Yummy」（「創意美食」）。翻查記錄，&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;今星期應停泊中環海濱，惟10月2日起多天未見營業<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n對「創意美食」打算離場，黃感驚訝及無奈，因「大師兄」與對方共用中央廚房，「而家每月蝕數萬元，如果佢離場，我哋成本又再增加。」"},{"pid":"92dcd20d50b91fd03d71b7294f397b185566ac70","tid":425574,"uid":35815,"like":10,"dislike":10,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T00:29:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"797b9f12b785db271e62a06f3f390bd5af3c37f5","tid":425574,"uid":49392,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T00:35:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>美食車係品客主打本土民生既提議<br />\n點知搞到屎咁<br />\n<br />\n但品客唔係有加持咩<br />\n點解無人去撐美食車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n而家個特首係777"},{"pid":"775501654ecf768fbd67310ffd9a4ec5ab7c801a","tid":425574,"uid":51720,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T00:37:39.000Z","msg":"仲有官僚制度（美食車要申領多個牌照，仲有多多限制）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfcb0240662f0c4d783425153dcb8d91750e81cf","tid":425574,"uid":35815,"like":41,"dislike":6,"score":35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T00:48:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b6e121e16d79130a21f8ebfe13b0ddbc08ba68dc","tid":425574,"uid":49392,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T00:51:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>美食車係品客主打本土民生既提議<br />\n點知搞到屎咁<br />\n<br />\n但品客唔係有加持咩<br />\n點解無人去撐美食車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/d